test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -4 == -8
 +  where -4 = <built-in function prod>([-4])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a18197fa000>([-8])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a18197fa000> = [[1], [1, -8], [-8, 1], [-8, 1, -8], [1], [1, -8], ...].count
